WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.457 --> 00:00:02.480
Good morning family, praise the Lord!

00:00:02.480 --> 00:00:03.830
How are you all doing today?

00:00:03.830 --> 00:00:05.420
Well, thank you for joining me.

00:00:05.420 --> 00:00:14.913
You know, I was praying this evening and the Lord spoke to me and said, 'Brandon, 2025 is going to be a good year for the believers.

00:00:14.913 --> 00:00:29.412
' I was looking over in the spirit and the Lord was allowing me to see the outpouring of healings, the demonstrations, and the manifestations of the Father.

00:00:29.412 --> 00:00:33.720
You all, we're about to see some of the most amazing things.

00:00:34.320 --> 00:00:50.880
I'm telling you, our forefathers—like even 200 or 300 years ago—the people who were looking forward to the Lord Jesus coming and thought he was coming in their timeframe, folks, we're about to see the Lord Jesus come.

00:00:51.280 --> 00:00:54.577
We're going to see a major harvest of souls.

00:00:54.902 --> 00:01:04.628
I know I keep telling you all this, and I've said it over and over; I probably sound like a broken record, but I need you to know it.

00:01:04.628 --> 00:01:15.982
I need you to have a deep revelation that God is about to do something, because he keeps telling me, 'Brandon, I'm about to show up and show off in your life.

00:01:15.982 --> 00:01:18.780
I want you to believe me for bigger.

00:01:18.780 --> 00:01:22.040
' This is the second time this week he said that.

00:01:22.040 --> 00:01:27.973
We are on the countdown: 5, 4, 3, 2, 1, liftoff!

00:01:28.484 --> 00:01:43.329
I'm telling you, a great move of God is about to hit this land like you have never seen.

00:02:01.491 --> 00:02:01.857
I'm telling you: exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:02:03.320 --> 00:02:05.747
It's time to believe God for bigger.

00:02:05.747 --> 00:02:13.467
Stretch your faith to believe exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:02:13.467 --> 00:02:18.050
He said, 'Brandon, it's going to be about the thinking.

00:02:18.050 --> 00:02:24.950
' I said this yesterday, but it just keeps bubbling inside of me, just believing.

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:31.629
I went to a Christmas party today and it was all I could do.

00:02:34.695 --> 00:03:01.274
I was sitting at the front, and it's probably because it's a prayer church—you know, our church has a lot of intercessory prayer that goes forth out of there—but I was sitting toward the front where they had the dinner, and I felt like travail was hitting me in the middle of the Christmas party.

00:03:13.246 --> 00:03:23.480
People were playing games and everything, and I'm looking, going, 'My goodness, I just feel like I could weep because of the intercession coming up out of my spirit to intercede for the lost and for what's coming.

00:03:23.480 --> 00:03:29.199
' When I came home, I started watching Billy Burke.

00:03:29.199 --> 00:03:40.400
I told my wife, 'I want to hear this sermon from Billy Burke,' because it was a healing thing.

00:03:45.940 --> 00:03:46.310
He was teaching healing and he just fans my flame.

00:03:57.897 --> 00:03:58.159
The words he speaks inspire me, and I just want to stay inspired.

00:03:58.159 --> 00:04:22.823
People were asking in the comment section—my son told me and my wife told me from the emails—people are saying, 'How, Brandon, do we have an intimate relationship with the Father?

00:04:22.823 --> 00:04:25.903
How do we get there?

00:04:25.903 --> 00:04:39.199
' When Diana shared the word she had from the Lord, it challenged a lot of you, and rightfully so.

00:04:43.805 --> 00:04:44.535
It challenged me and it challenged her.

00:04:44.535 --> 00:04:57.039
It wasn't just that he was speaking it to us and we let it fall on deaf ears.

00:04:59.420 --> 00:05:05.060
He was talking to us too, because we need to come up higher.

00:05:05.060 --> 00:05:12.860
Diana and I have talked about that word a lot lately.

00:05:12.860 --> 00:05:21.440
Going to a place of intimacy with the Father is not a hard thing.

00:05:21.440 --> 00:05:29.719
We make it hard because we think God is way out there.

00:05:43.370 --> 00:05:43.660
Of course, God is a holy God, a big God, the ultimate in everything, but he's small enough to live in each one of us.

00:05:43.660 --> 00:05:57.199
It's like the Imperials sang: 'My God is a big God who walks among the mountains, but he's small enough to live in me.

00:05:57.199 --> 00:06:04.466
' God is small enough to live in you.

00:06:04.466 --> 00:06:18.070
He lives on the inside of us, and we make it difficult whenever we have all these religious thoughts like Pharisees.

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:23.399
We think God doesn't want to spend time with us.

00:06:23.399 --> 00:06:36.200
We have all these stupid thoughts because the devil tries to put those negative words in; he comes like a roaring lion seeking whom he may devour.

00:06:38.782 --> 00:06:44.897
He's looking for those he can pick off—the ones who are lukewarm, cold, or not hot.

00:06:44.897 --> 00:06:57.308
Like Billy Burke said tonight when I was watching him, there's a river of water that flows out of us.

00:06:58.451 --> 00:07:05.360
Have you ever seen a fire hose when the fire department is putting out a big fire?

00:07:07.840 --> 00:07:10.880
A major fire hose will knock you down.

00:07:16.563 --> 00:07:23.377
The devil is looking to see if there is a major fire hose, a major river flowing out of you.

00:07:23.377 --> 00:07:38.427
When you are standing there, he's looking to see if you have it or not, because any Christian who is on fire, he's going to run away from.

00:07:38.427 --> 00:07:47.800
James says that if we submit ourselves unto God and resist the devil, he will flee in terror.

00:08:01.989 --> 00:08:11.200
So he's looking for who has that fire, who has that inward knowing of who they are in Christ—that you can do all things through Christ who strengthens you.

00:08:11.200 --> 00:08:23.280
He's out there, his eyes roaming to and fro, and he's going, 'I want to see who I can devour.

00:08:23.280 --> 00:08:31.908
' But he can't devour the one whose foundation and house is built on the solid rock.

00:08:31.908 --> 00:08:47.385
He knows whom he can devour and whom he can't; that's why he's seeking, because there are some folks he knows he can't mess with.

00:08:47.385 --> 00:08:53.747
Those are the ones who are on fire for Jesus.

00:08:53.747 --> 00:09:00.160
So how do you get on fire for Jesus?

00:09:04.645 --> 00:09:06.920
He made it so a child can have a relationship with him.

00:09:06.920 --> 00:09:11.253
He made it so every born-again Christian has the ability.

00:09:11.253 --> 00:09:18.800
We all have 24 hours in a day, seven days a week.

00:09:35.800 --> 00:09:39.280
Not one of us has any more and not one has anything less, but everyone has a choice of how much time they're going to spend with him today.

00:09:47.340 --> 00:09:47.610
You may say, 'Well, I'm so busy.

00:09:47.610 --> 00:09:59.884
I've got to go to the gym, I've got to go to work, I've got to come home and watch my favorite TV program.

00:09:59.884 --> 00:10:19.080
' Then you have some people who go to the gym and look like Arnold Schwarzenegger, or any athlete, but everyone has a choice of how they want to spend their time.

00:10:25.942 --> 00:10:28.990
If you want to be a spiritual giant, you have to do what a spiritual giant does.

00:10:28.990 --> 00:10:32.560
You've got to get in the word.

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:39.498
Everybody has the opportunity to get in the word.

00:10:41.120 --> 00:10:49.593
You can get your Bible out, look at those scriptures, read a couple of passages, and memorize them.

00:11:01.320 --> 00:11:01.680
It's not going to be a microwave; it's going to be a slow-cook oven.

00:11:01.680 --> 00:11:06.742
Find one or two scriptures and memorize them over the week.

00:11:06.742 --> 00:11:12.052
If you memorize ten scriptures over the year, think about the math on that.

00:11:12.052 --> 00:11:23.600
If you get those down inside of your heart within a two-year period, think about where you'll be.

00:11:23.600 --> 00:11:30.818
Praying in the spirit: I had a counselor when I worked for Rhema Ministry.

00:11:30.818 --> 00:11:43.424
She said if you pray in the spirit and talk in tongues for 30 minutes a day, your life will never be the same.

00:11:43.424 --> 00:11:46.705
Then increase it to an hour.

00:11:46.705 --> 00:11:55.960
Brother Kenneth Hagin talked about praying for an hour or two in tongues, in the mornings and the evenings.

00:11:55.960 --> 00:12:09.930
That's why I've tried to tell you all: if your flesh eats breakfast, lunch, and dinner, try to feed your spirit breakfast, lunch, and dinner.

00:12:09.930 --> 00:12:21.020
Feeding your spirit three times a day with small passages doesn't have to be reading the whole Bible.

00:12:21.020 --> 00:12:31.260
People get on these religious kicks and say, 'I'm going to read the Bible in a year.

00:12:31.260 --> 00:12:34.516
' Fine, but did you learn anything?

00:12:34.516 --> 00:12:45.800
Did the word change you, or did you just do it to brag about it?

00:12:45.800 --> 00:12:49.844
Find scriptures that will change you.

00:12:49.844 --> 00:13:00.120
The Bible says, 'If ye abide in me and my words remain in you, you shall ask what you will and it shall be done.

00:13:00.120 --> 00:13:12.511
' If you're getting that word down inside of you and feeding on it, that's when your prayers get answered.

00:13:12.511 --> 00:13:26.392
If you're not getting your prayers answered, maybe it's because you don't have enough word inside of you.

00:13:29.120 --> 00:13:42.930
The more word you put on the inside, the more you're going to see things change, because that's when your prayers are going to get answered.

00:13:42.930 --> 00:13:47.664
Prayer changes things, but it's the scripture you know that's going to change you.

00:13:47.664 --> 00:13:55.218
People say, 'I've got a devil,' and 'I don't know how to get free.

00:13:55.218 --> 00:14:03.750
' The Bible says you will know the truth and the truth will set you free.

00:14:04.729 --> 00:14:13.399
The more you get inside the word of God, the more it's going to change you from glory to glory.

00:14:13.399 --> 00:14:18.519
How do you become intimate with the Lord?

00:14:19.1000 --> 00:14:23.600
You get intimate with the word.

00:14:23.600 --> 00:14:32.009
When you get the word inside of you, your prayer life is going to change.

00:14:32.009 --> 00:14:37.320
Faith comes by hearing, and hearing by the word of God.

00:14:45.473 --> 00:14:48.240
Your faith is going to grow, you're going to be intimate with the Father, and it's going to change your life.

00:14:55.135 --> 00:15:00.919
The Bible says that his sheep will hear his voice and a stranger's voice they will not follow.

00:15:00.919 --> 00:15:09.120
But you don't know that until you get inside that word.

00:15:09.120 --> 00:15:13.704
Have a revelation of that.

00:15:15.991 --> 00:15:25.440
The entrance of his word brings forth light, because God is light and in him there is no darkness at all.

00:15:25.440 --> 00:15:33.169
The more you get light—which is the word of God—the more you are intimate with the word by reading it.

00:15:34.194 --> 00:15:34.959
You say it's boring?

00:15:34.959 --> 00:15:37.937
No, it will change you.

00:15:40.237 --> 00:15:50.639
It is life to those that find it and health to all their flesh.

00:15:50.639 --> 00:15:55.789
Seek and you will find; knock and the door will be opened unto you.

00:15:55.789 --> 00:16:01.508
His words are life and health to your flesh.

00:16:01.508 --> 00:16:21.340
If you are bound by a demonic force, the Bible says if you don't fill your temple up, the devil you cast out comes back for a season to see if you're filled.

00:16:21.340 --> 00:16:32.680
If not, he comes back with eight more of his buddies and you're worse off.

00:16:33.960 --> 00:16:40.275
The word is what keeps you free and makes you free.

00:16:44.759 --> 00:16:50.940
You have to have a foundation of the word of God in your life to change you.

00:16:50.940 --> 00:16:58.319
People say, 'How do I have an intimate relationship with the Father?

00:16:58.319 --> 00:17:04.747
' It's by feeding on the word of God and praying.

00:17:04.747 --> 00:17:10.439
If your word level is low, keep your word level high.

00:17:10.988 --> 00:17:17.035
The more you meditate on that word, it will change you from the inside out.

00:17:17.035 --> 00:17:27.902
You're going to hear his voice, you're going to know him, and you're going to become intimate with him.

00:17:27.902 --> 00:17:36.902
Then you pray and you obey, and the Lord will speak to you.

00:17:43.955 --> 00:17:48.857
The more you pray in tongues—if you need to get baptized in the Holy Ghost, just pray in English until you do.

00:17:52.232 --> 00:18:04.723
The more you hang around me, you're going to get baptized in the Holy Ghost because I believe in it: the Holy Ghost and fire.

00:18:17.955 --> 00:18:19.304
The burden-removing, yoke-destroying power is on the inside of you when you get filled with the Holy Ghost.

00:18:19.304 --> 00:18:23.048
I practice it too much.

00:18:23.048 --> 00:18:30.110
The Holy Spirit dwells inside of me richly by faith.

00:18:30.110 --> 00:18:46.159
Out of my belly shall flow rivers of living water, and that's what quenches all the fiery darts of the wicked.

00:19:06.320 --> 00:19:06.620
The name of the Lord is a strong tower, and the righteous run into it and they are safe.

00:19:06.920 --> 00:19:12.624
I want to encourage you today to make the word of God a priority.

00:19:12.624 --> 00:19:15.420
Find scriptures that minister to you.

00:19:15.420 --> 00:19:27.457
Find a version of the Bible you understand, like the Amplified or the New Living Translation, so it becomes life to you.

00:19:27.457 --> 00:19:32.615
That's how you get intimate with the Father.

00:19:32.615 --> 00:19:38.794
The more you read, pray, and obey, the closer you become.

00:19:38.794 --> 00:20:03.662
Miss Sue used to tell me that if you just pray 30 minutes a day in tongues—start with 10 or 15 minutes, then work up to 30—praying in the spirit with a brand new tongue, it's a beautiful song.

00:20:22.533 --> 00:20:22.827
That's what's going to change you.

00:20:22.827 --> 00:20:32.544
You'll start to hear the voice of the Lord, and he'll start giving you signs, wonders, dreams, and visions.

00:20:32.544 --> 00:20:40.053
At the end of 2025, your life will have radically changed.

00:20:40.053 --> 00:20:44.497
Try it for a year.

00:20:44.497 --> 00:20:57.419
Find scriptures for healing, deliverance, your marriage—whatever you are believing for—and use them as a sword against the devil.

00:20:57.419 --> 00:21:12.240
God said to me, 'Brandon, I'm ready to do some big stuff for my kids if they'll just believe me.

00:21:12.240 --> 00:21:22.029
' This will be an amazing year for you and your children: spiritually, physically, financially, mentally, and emotionally.

00:21:22.029 --> 00:21:24.667
2025: believe God for big.

00:21:24.667 --> 00:21:32.331
We're almost done with 2024, but believe him even more in 2025.

00:21:32.331 --> 00:21:43.970
I'm not worried about what's going on in the world right now—the wars and rumors of wars.

00:21:43.970 --> 00:21:47.190
I'm focused on you today.

00:21:47.190 --> 00:21:51.999
What are you believing God for in 2025?

00:21:51.999 --> 00:22:06.747
I'm going to keep on this for a bit: believing God for the supernatural, exceedingly abundantly above all that you dare ask or think.

00:22:06.747 --> 00:22:08.320
Let's pray.

00:22:20.329 --> 00:22:20.707
I hope this blessed you.

00:22:20.707 --> 00:22:26.679
Let's believe God for something big for you.

00:22:26.679 --> 00:22:34.685
Don't keep putting off for tomorrow what you believe for now.

00:22:40.120 --> 00:22:45.159
Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and the evidence of things not seen.

00:22:45.159 --> 00:22:56.440
He corrects me all the time: 'Brandon, why are you believing for tomorrow?

00:22:56.440 --> 00:23:06.587
' I'll be in the church praying and think, 'Maybe that'll come in a couple days.

00:23:06.587 --> 00:23:13.120
' He'll say, 'Brandon, hold on, believe for now.

00:23:13.120 --> 00:23:27.440
' Now faith is the substance of things hoped for and the evidence of things not seen yet.

00:23:27.440 --> 00:23:40.583
We stagger not at the promise of God through unbelief, but are strong in faith, giving glory to God.

00:23:40.583 --> 00:23:49.931
Be fully persuaded that what God has promised, he is able also to perform.

00:23:49.931 --> 00:23:53.804
Father, I thank you for the supernatural.

00:23:53.804 --> 00:24:00.360
Everything the Bible says I can have, I will have.

00:24:00.360 --> 00:24:11.453
Everything the Bible says I can do, I will do, uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:24:23.834 --> 00:24:24.140
I believe today that they are delivered and set free.

00:24:32.086 --> 00:24:34.331
I thank you, Lord, that they will know the truth and the truth will make them free.

00:24:38.519 --> 00:24:42.039
I speak life, increase, and favor over their lives.

00:24:42.039 --> 00:24:46.480
Everything they put their hands to will prosper.

00:24:46.480 --> 00:24:59.920
This is a time like never before where you said, 'Brandon, I want to show up and show off in their lives.

00:24:59.920 --> 00:25:09.509
' I believe it is a time for healing and wholeness over marriages.

00:25:13.279 --> 00:25:13.519
We call your marriage blessed and favored.

00:25:27.910 --> 00:25:28.340
I thank you, Lord, for deliverance from pornography.

00:25:35.164 --> 00:25:35.409
You foul devil from hell, get off of them!

00:25:38.020 --> 00:25:44.265
We say they are delivered from the spirit of lust and pornography in the name of Jesus.

00:25:44.265 --> 00:25:58.184
Delivered from alcoholism, tobacco, and drug addiction; from abuse, anorexia, and bulimia, I say in the name of Jesus they are free.

00:25:58.184 --> 00:26:06.871
I thank you, Lord, that they are delivered from PTSD and strongholds of the mind.

00:26:06.871 --> 00:26:16.181
From Alzheimer's and dementia, they will have sound sleep and wake up refreshed.

00:26:16.181 --> 00:26:21.411
Their youth is renewed like the eagles'.

00:26:21.411 --> 00:26:30.395
Their eyes will not grow dim; there are no cataracts, no glaucoma.

00:26:35.835 --> 00:26:36.968
We decree 20/20 vision in the name of Jesus.

00:26:37.480 --> 00:26:47.285
We thank you that the fire of the Holy Ghost delivers them from satanic bondage.

00:26:50.389 --> 00:26:52.039
We call their ears to pop open.

00:26:52.039 --> 00:26:57.890
Even as they grow older, they will not lose their hearing.

00:26:57.890 --> 00:27:04.457
I thank you that glory is restoring their organs.

00:27:06.555 --> 00:27:17.462
I thank you for the blessing of the Lord, that the harvesters and the sowers are going hand in hand.

00:27:17.462 --> 00:27:22.191
Seed time and harvest time is being shortened now.

00:27:22.191 --> 00:27:25.603
Acceleration is coming to your seeds.

00:27:25.603 --> 00:27:32.017
Every seed they sow, come forth in the name of Jesus.

00:27:32.017 --> 00:27:34.680
Abundance is on your life today.

00:27:34.680 --> 00:27:40.650
They are no longer broke, busted, and disgusted, but have overflow.

00:27:43.480 --> 00:27:52.589
Father, we call Trump to be filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost, with a godly cabinet.

00:27:52.589 --> 00:28:11.159
I thank you for our economy and everything you showed me about BlackRock and Jerome Powell, and the interest rates, and what you warned me about them trying to sink the economy.

00:28:11.159 --> 00:28:17.055
Satan, get your hands off of our economy!

00:28:30.440 --> 00:28:30.994
We have authority over you.

00:28:30.994 --> 00:28:34.320
Crypto will soar.

00:28:40.464 --> 00:28:42.919
The things God has for his body will soar in 2025.

00:28:44.800 --> 00:28:45.760
We thank you for supernatural abundance.

00:28:59.775 --> 00:28:59.960
The stock market and cryptocurrency are turning around.

00:29:08.213 --> 00:29:08.427
We will not have a major economic downturn right now; it is delayed.

00:29:08.427 --> 00:29:17.629
Father, I thank you that Elon Musk is born again and radically saved.

00:29:20.500 --> 00:29:33.133
I call forth regulation over crypto and I thank you, Lord, that Jerome Powell and the Fed will not mess this up anymore.

00:29:43.267 --> 00:29:43.498
The devil is trying to rear his head, but we still have work to do.

00:29:43.498 --> 00:29:47.440
We call for blessing over this nation and favor.

00:29:47.440 --> 00:29:53.089
Tomorrow is going to be a good day.

00:29:53.089 --> 00:30:00.695
We call our unsaved loved ones saved and filled with the Holy Ghost.

00:30:00.695 --> 00:30:14.813
If you want to know how to draw close to God, read 'The Ultimate Voice' by Oral Roberts; that book is amazing.

00:30:14.813 --> 00:30:17.900
Thank you for joining us.

00:30:17.900 --> 00:30:25.089
Our South Korean channel is exploding, and we have a China channel now.

00:30:25.089 --> 00:30:32.000
If you are new here and speak Chinese or Korean, go join those channels so you don't have to read the subtitles.

