We appreciate the support on this channel.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Please click the subscribe button, the notification button, and comment below.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
It helps us get in the algorithm and spread the gospel throughout the whole world.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.850
Asia is about to have a major revival, especially South Korea.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:03.500
God bless you all, and we'll see you again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.900
Remember to put a smile on your face and a song in your heart.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Jesus loves you, and we love you.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.450
Look up, for your redemption draws nigh.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.000
Bye-bye.
